summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending pages 151 and 165 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone property located at 6550 32nd Avenue S.W. (High Point Garden Community) from Multifamily Lowrise 1 to a combination of Lowrise 2, Lowrise 4, and Neighborhood Commercial 2 with a 40' height limit; and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Seattle Housing Authority, C.F. 305400, Application. 2105600)
